Rocia takes your everyday elegance to the next level of style through this pair of trendy heels which is crafted in a fusion of brown and beige. The textured sole and padded footbed ensures that your feet is given the desired comfort and support when walking. You can team these Rocia heels with a trendy kurta and leggings.

Rocia devotes meticulous care and excellent craftsmanship into its wide range of chic and trendy footwear that encompasses a youthful zest and vibrancy in order to offer nothing but the best for the contemporary woman.
